---
title: Smart Sesame-Crusted Turkey Rissoles with Carrot Mash and Honey-Soy Drizzle
description: These turkey rissoles get browned in the pan to give the sesame seeds a nutty flavour. A honey-soy sauce drizzled over buttery mashed carrots and tender-crisp roasted broccoli adds a satisfying sweet-savoury element to this 'smart' meal!

